{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "原初之力 第24章 4-3 原初之风",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "抵达“龙之墓”的一行见到了\\n由“起始之龙”而生的原初耶梦加得。\\n而原初耶梦加得则是为了应对\\n“起始之人”的再次复活\\n而将意志的碎片留于此处。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "唉……往哪儿走都是沙漠……\\n那个叫“龙之墓”的还有多远啊？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "据说就在这一带……\\n但我也不清楚具体的位置。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "这里原本是个巨大的湖泊。\\n相传湖底沉睡着\\n原初之龙的坟墓。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "勒福克斯的古老传说中\\n也有提到这里是众龙的\\n转生之地。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "那耶梦加得还有穆穆他们\\n也都是在这里转生的吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "我有记忆以来就一直身在火山，\\n可没来过这种地方啊？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "一切生命皆起源于魔力而又归于魔力。\\n这方面我们比人类更加明显。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "布伦希尔德生于火焰，\\n自然会有与其相符之地。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "那为什么还说这里是\\n龙的转生之地啊？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "传说不一定就是真相。\\n就算所言非虚，也有可能在\\n口口相传的过程中被夸大。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "但这里确实沉睡着什么。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "你能感觉到？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "来到这里后，\\n我就一直能够感受到某种召唤……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "召……唤？\\n可我什么都没听到啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "耶梦加得都这么说的话，\\n这里也许真的有什么。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "为了确认这点，\\n我们也必须继续前进。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "龙的转生之地吗……\\n说到底龙的转生\\n究竟怎么一回事啊？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "龙与其说是生命，不如说是自然。\\n也可以说是大自然意志的化身。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "其中也有更为接近纯粹魔力的化身……\\n被称作五龙的我们就是这样。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "向我们这样本质更接近于魔力的龙，\\n是不在生命的循环之内的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "生命的循环？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "出生、成长、繁衍、衰老……\\n我们并不会经历这样的循环。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "诶？那穆穆也是？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "嗯。我无父无母，\\n有记忆以来就一直是\\n你见过的龙的样子了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "但我们也会与其他生命\\n一样迎来死亡。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "死亡之际，我们的身体和意志会\\n化为魔力，然后全新的耶梦加得\\n会在某处诞生。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "全新的耶梦加得……\\n会与现在的你完全不同吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "样貌和力量应该和我一样吧，\\n思维方式估计也差不多。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "但会失去之前的记忆。\\n所以我基本不记得转生之前的经历。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "那你如果转生的话，\\n岂不是也会把我们都……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "应该会就此遗忘吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "也就是说我所认识的那个\\n耶梦加得将不复存在吗……\\n这样也太让人伤心了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "我以前可是受了耶梦加得\\n不少照顾呢……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "是吗……不好意思，\\n很遗憾我没有这个记忆。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "毕竟1000年前的耶梦加得\\n不是现在的耶梦加得啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "不过这也确实没办法。\\n只是正因为许多地方都很像，\\n反而让人感到难受。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "的确，被一直以来\\n都并肩同行的大家所遗忘，\\n是挺让人悲伤的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "亲爱的！不要担心！\\n无论发生什么，\\n我都不会忘记你的！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "我们的爱是永恒的！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "哈、哈哈……谢谢你，穆穆。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "但不知为何……\\n耶梦加得现在的样貌和\\n我所认识的碧龙有些不同。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "是因为转生而\\n失去了力量吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "也许吧……\\n虽然理论上转生时不会失去力量，\\n但事实却是力量不如从前。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "如果能在这里解开这个谜团……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "我等你很久了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01",
                "100001_09",
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "你是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "我名为耶梦加得。\\n与我同有风之名的龙啊，\\n我已等候你多时。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "耶梦加得！？\\n难道……这是耶梦加得\\n转生前的样子？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "倒是和我认识的耶梦加得很像……\\n真令人怀念啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "但又似乎有哪点不太一样……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210131_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "我乃风之始祖，\\n由“起始之龙”而生的原初耶梦加得。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "也就是我的始祖吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "那你就是曾经对抗从异界尽头\\n归来的“起始之人”并将其\\n再次封印的五龙之一吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210131_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "始祖耶梦加得",
            "context": "正是。\\n如今我只是意志和记忆的残渣，\\n来自远古之风的余音。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210131_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "始祖耶梦加得",
            "context": "因那弗至而至之日\\n而在此等待新风。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "弗至而至之日……\\n你的意思是——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "始祖耶梦加得",
            "context": "“起始之人”归来之日。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "始祖耶梦加得",
            "context": "我将意志留存于此，\\n是为传承那远古的记忆。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "原来如此……\\n所以这里才会被称作\\n龙的沉睡之地“龙之墓”啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "也就是说我们的目的相同咯。\\n那就好办了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我想你应该已经有所察觉，\\n“起始之人”——泽诺斯\\n已经在这个世界复活了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我们正是为了寻求\\n与其对抗的手段才来到这里。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "原初碧龙，请你告诉我们，\\n当初的你们是如何对抗“起始之人”的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_06_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}